# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200007> (alveolar border of mandible)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200007> "A zone of bone organ forming the superior margin of the mandibular body, bearing the dental alveoli (sockets) that house the roots of the lower teeth.")
