# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200012> (anterior tubercle of first cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200012> "A skeletal element projection situated on the anterior midline surface of the anterior arch of the atlas (C1), serving as the attachment point for the anterior longitudinal ligament and the longus colli muscle.")
