# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200026> (coccygeal cornu of coccyx)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200026> "A skeletal element projection arising from the superior surface of the first coccygeal segment as a pair of upward-projecting rounded processes that articulate with the sacral cornua to form the sacrococcygeal joint.")
