# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200038> (facet of eleventh rib)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200038> "A zone of bone organ on the head of the eleventh rib that forms a single, undivided articular surface for articulation exclusively with the body of the eleventh thoracic vertebra. Because the eleventh rib is an atypical floating rib, its head bears only one facet rather than the two demifacets found on typical ribs.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200038> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
