# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200041> (facet of twelfth rib)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200041> "A zone of bone organ on the head of the twelfth rib forming a single, rounded articular surface that articulates exclusively with the body of the twelfth thoracic vertebra. The twelfth rib is a floating atypical rib and, like the eleventh, has an undivided head with no superior demifacet.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200041> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
