# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200045> (foramen ovale of sphenoid bone)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200045> "A bone foramen located in the greater wing of the sphenoid bone, posterior to the foramen rotundum and lateral to the foramen lacerum; it transmits the mandibular nerve (cranial nerve V3), the accessory meningeal artery, and the lesser petrosal nerve.")
