AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200047> "A crest projecting from the internal surface of the frontal bone in the midline, descending from the foramen cecum toward the groove for the superior sagittal sinus. It provides attachment for the falx cerebri.")
