# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200053> (greater palatine canal of maxilla)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200053> "A bone foramen forming a vertical canal at the junction of the maxilla and perpendicular plate of the palatine bone that transmits the greater palatine nerve and descending palatine vessels from the pterygopalatine fossa to the hard palate.")
