# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200086> (inferior articular facet of fifth cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200086> "A zone of bone organ on the inferior articular process of the fifth cervical vertebra (C5), presenting an obliquely oriented smooth articular surface directed anteroinferiorly and laterally to articulate with the superior articular facet of C6.")
