# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200088> (inferior articular facet of first cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200088> "A zone of bone organ located on the inferior aspect of the lateral mass of the atlas (C1), presenting a flat to slightly concave articular surface that articulates with the superior articular facet of the axis to form the lateral atlantoaxial joint.")
