# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200103> (inferior articular process of first cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200103> "A process of vertebra projecting inferiorly from the lateral mass of the atlas (C1), bearing a smooth articular facet that forms the lateral atlantoaxial joint with the superior articular process of the axis; it is positioned further anteriorly than in typical cervical vertebrae.")
