# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200116> (internal occipital protuberance of squamous part of occipital bone)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200116> "A skeletal element projection on the internal surface of the squamous occipital bone at the center of the cruciform eminence, marking the confluence of sinuses where the superior sagittal, straight, and occipital sinuses meet.")
