# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200121> (lamina of first cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200121> "A vertebra lamina forming the posterior curved plate of the atlas (C1) that completes the posterior arch, connecting the lateral masses to the posterior tubercle; it is thinner and more curved than laminae of typical cervical vertebrae, lacking a spinous process.")
