# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200127> (linea terminalis of sacrum)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200127> "A zone of bone organ forming the sacral contribution to the linea terminalis, constituting the posterior arc of the pelvic brim and demarcating the boundary between the greater and lesser pelvis at the level of the sacral promontory and alae.")
