# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200134> (mandibular angle of mandible)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200134> "A zone of bone organ at the postero-inferior junction of the mandibular body and ramus, providing attachment for the masseter muscle on its lateral surface and the medial pterygoid muscle on its medial surface.")
