# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200135> (mandibular foramen of mandible)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200135> "A bone foramen on the medial surface of the mandibular ramus, guarded anteriorly by the lingula, through which the inferior alveolar nerve and vessels enter the mandibular canal.")
