# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200144> (mental protuberance of mandible)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200144> "A triangular skeletal element projection forming the prominence of the bony chin at the anterior midline of the mandibular body, bounded laterally by the mental tubercles and considered a defining morphological feature of modern Homo sapiens.")
