# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200170> (perpendicular plate of ethmoid bone)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200170> "A zone of bone organ forming a thin, flat, vertical midline lamina that descends from the cribriform plate to articulate inferiorly with the septal cartilage and the vomer, contributing to the bony nasal septum.")
