# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200174> (posterior gluteal line of ilium of os coxa)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200174> "A zone of bone organ forming a curved ridge near the posterior margin of the gluteal surface of the ilium of the os coxa (innominate bone), extending from the iliac crest toward the greater sciatic notch and demarcating the small posterior area of origin of the gluteus maximus from the larger area of the gluteus medius.")
