# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200181> (pterygoid hamulus of sphenoid bone)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200181> "A skeletal element projection forming the slender, hook-like inferior tip of the medial pterygoid plate of the sphenoid bone, curving laterally and inferiorly; it serves as a pulley around which the tendon of the tensor veli palatini muscle turns before spreading into the soft palate.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200181> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
