# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200186> (radial fossa of humerus)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200186> "A bone fossa situated on the anterior surface of the lateral distal humerus, immediately superior to the capitulum, that receives the anterior rim of the head of the radius during full flexion of the elbow at the humeroradial joint.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200186> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
