# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200191> (sacral cornu of sacrum)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200191> "A skeletal element projection at the inferior margin of the sacral hiatus, one of a pair of downward-projecting bony processes representing the inferior articular processes of S5 that articulate with the coccygeal cornua and serve as palpable landmarks for caudal epidural anaesthesia.")
