# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200198> (scapular notch of scapula)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200198> "A semicircular bone foramen on the superior border of the scapula, medial to the base of the coracoid process, through which the suprascapular nerve passes beneath the superior transverse scapular ligament to enter the supraspinous fossa.")
