# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200199> (scapular spine of scapula)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200199> "A prominent, triangular skeletal element projection arising from the posterior surface of the scapula and running obliquely from the medial border to the acromion, dividing the posterior scapular surface into the supraspinous and infraspinous fossae and providing attachment for the trapezius and deltoid muscles.")
