# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200201> (shaft of first distal phalanx of hand)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200201> "A zone of bone organ comprising the flattened, tapering body of the distal phalanx of the thumb, lying between the base and the ungual tuberosity and providing dorsal and palmar surfaces for attachment of the nail bed and soft tissue pulp.")
