# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200207> (spinous process of second cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200207> "A neural spine projecting posteriorly and inferiorly from the vertebral arch of the axis (C2), characteristically large and bifid at its tip, serving as a palpable landmark and providing attachment for the ligamentum nuchae, semispinalis cervicis, and inferior oblique capitis muscles.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200207> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
