# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200208> (sternal angle of sternum)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200208> "A zone of bone organ forming the transverse ridge on the anterior surface of the sternum at the manubriosternal junction, palpable as a distinct anterior angulation; it lies at the level of the second costal cartilage and marks the plane separating the superior from the inferior mediastinum.")
