# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200213> (sternal end of fourth rib)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200213> "A zone of bone organ forming the anterior extremity of the fourth rib that connects to the costal cartilage of the fourth rib. The fourth rib is a true rib whose costal cartilage articulates directly with the lateral border of the sternum, typically at the level of the sternal angle.")
