# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200215> (sternal end of second rib)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200215> "A zone of bone organ forming the anterior extremity of the second rib that connects to the costal cartilage of the second rib. The second rib is a true rib whose costal cartilage articulates with the sternum at the sternal angle (angle of Louis), the junction between the manubrium and the body of the sternum.")
