# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200219> (sternal end of third rib)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200219> "A zone of bone organ forming the anterior extremity of the third rib that connects to the costal cartilage of the third rib. The third rib is a true rib whose costal cartilage articulates with the lateral border of the body of the sternum between the second and fourth costal notches.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200219> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
