# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200250> (superior articular process of first cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200250> "A process of vertebra forming the broad lateral mass of the atlas (C1) on its superior aspect, bearing the kidney-shaped concave facet that receives the occipital condyle to form the atlanto-occipital joint, enabling nodding movements of the head.")
