# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200260> (supraorbital notch or foramen of frontal bone)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200260> "A bone foramen or notch in the supraorbital margin of the frontal bone, positioned approximately one-third of the way along the margin from its medial end. It transmits the supraorbital nerve and vessels to the forehead and scalp.")
