# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200265> (transverse costal facet of eighth thoracic vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200265> "A zone of bone organ located on the anterior surface of the transverse process of the eighth thoracic vertebra, articulating with the tubercle of the eighth rib at the costotransverse joint. The transverse processes are progressively shorter and more posteriorly directed at this level, and the facet is correspondingly reduced compared to those of upper thoracic vertebrae.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200265> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
