# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200269> (transverse costal facet of fourth thoracic vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200269> "A zone of bone organ located on the anterior surface of the transverse process of the fourth thoracic vertebra, presenting as a smooth concave articular area that articulates with the tubercle of the fourth rib at the costotransverse joint. Together with the body demifacets it completes the bony articulation of rib 4 with the thoracic column.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200269> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
