# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200279> (trigeminal impression of petrous part of temporal bone)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200279> "A zone of bone organ forming a shallow depression near the apex of the petrous part of the temporal bone on its anterosuperior surface. It lodges the trigeminal ganglion (Gasserian ganglion) within Meckel's cave and is covered by a fold of dura mater.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200279> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
