# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200295> (vertebral arch of fourth cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200295> "A neural arch forming the posterior bony ring of the fourth cervical vertebra (C4), composed of two pedicles and two laminae enclosing the vertebral foramen; it bears a bifid spinous process posteriorly and the zygapophyseal articular processes laterally.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200295> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
