# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200299> (vertebral arch of second cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200299> "A neural arch forming the posterior bony ring of the axis (C2), composed of two robust pedicles and two broad laminae; it bears the characteristically large bifid spinous process posteriorly and supports the superior articular processes that articulate with the atlas.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200299> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
