# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200302> (vertebral arch of seventh cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200302> "A neural arch forming the posterior bony ring of the seventh cervical vertebra (C7), composed of two pedicles and two laminae; it bears the long non-bifid vertebra prominens spinous process posteriorly, marking the transition to the thoracic spine.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200302> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
