# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200304> (vertebral arch of sixth cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200304> "A neural arch forming the posterior bony ring of the sixth cervical vertebra (C6), composed of two pedicles and two laminae; it bears a bifid spinous process posteriorly and provides attachment for the semispinalis and multifidus muscles.")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.org/dc/terms/date> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200304> "2026-03-19T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)
