# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200307> (vertebral arch of third cervical vertebra)

AnnotationAssertion(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_1200307> "A neural arch forming the posterior bony ring of the third cervical vertebra (C3), composed of two pedicles and two laminae enclosing the vertebral foramen; it bears a small bifid spinous process posteriorly and the zygapophyseal articular processes laterally.")
